      "date": "2014-11-06 00:05:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nThe patch itself looks good. But please refresh it to resolve the issue mentioned in the comment in lfsck_engine.c.\n\nAbout \"-C\" option, it works, because it is specified in the variable:\nchar *optstring = \"Ac::C::e:hM:n::ors:t:w:\";\n\nBut \"--create_mdtobj\" is missing, then only short option works, but long option failed.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
